path::Iter::<'a>::as_path.doc:
Extracts a slice corresponding to the portion of the path remaining for iteration.

# Examples

```
use std::path::Path;

let mut iter = Path::new("/tmp/foo/bar.txt").iter();
iter.next();
iter.next();

assert_eq!(Path::new("foo/bar.txt"), iter.as_path());
```

